title: Weds Post Show (10-19-22)

description:
Why it’s the best time to buy your plane tickets right now for holiday travel. A woman who was fired at for returning a package. A priest who was car jacked. A school that was shut down because it’s radioactive. Bobby shares a “Tell Me Something Bad”. Raymundo got married to a dinner with members of Congress.
